@node "About" "About PicScaler"
 Displays program completion date, author name address, and voice & email
 phone numbers.

 The keyboard shortcut is Right-Amiga-A.
@endnode
@node "Quit" "Quit PicScaler"
 Close any open files and exit PicScaler.

 The keyboard shortcut is Right-Amiga-Q
@endnode
@node "Prefs" "Save Preferences"

 Saves the following data to files in ENV:DFD/ and ENVARC:DFD/. The next
 time you run PicScaler this data will be read in and uses as your
 defaults.

   o  PicScaler window position on Workbench.

   o  "Scale to" and "Save as" Button Settings.

   o  Path you chose in the Load Picture file requester.

   o  Path you chose in the Save Scaled file requester.

  The keyboard shortcut is Right-Amiga-S.
@endnode

